  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf ,\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Cannabis, heroin and ice distributors nabbed in oil queues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Batapola Police arrested a man on suspicion of carrying three items in a suitcase on the main line last night (Jan. 26) at Gonapinuwala on suspicion of giving stimulants to those who had been sleeping in oil queues in front of petrol stations for several days.",
        "Police said that all the three items seized were cannabis, heroin and ice in the suspect's possession.",
        "The suspect was found in possession of 1.660 kilograms of cannabis, 7.600 grams of heroin and 6,300 grams of ice valued at around Rs. 1.5 million, police said.",
        "A Batapol police official said it was the first time that all three main drugs had been found in the possession of the same person by his police station.",
        "According to the police, the suspect had been going to petrol stations for several days and nights and had been carrying on the racket.",
        "Batapola OIC Janaka Sampath and other officers are conducting further investigations."
      ],
